OL,6,     FMonty the dog is in danger. Mack
OL,7,     Fis livid. A crisis of conscience
OL,8,     Ffor Kerry and Caleb.
OL,9,G1540 Coronation Street
OL,10,     FThe Driscolls pray for justice as
OL,11,     FMegan's verdict is delivered, Abi
OL,12,     Fidentifies her evasive landlord,
OL,13,     FSam makes peace with Nick, and
OL,14,     FHope and Ruby plan a surprise for
OL,15,     FTyrone.
